snippet.title: StrayShot's new map: Urban Ruins l Official Teaser
snippet.description:
Today, we're revealing a cool preview of
StrayShot's new map: Urban Ruins. It's like stepping into a world after everything went crazy, with broken buildings and underground passages where you'll battle it out with your team. 


Watch the teaser to see the awesome details of this awesome place where every corner is packed with action.

But wait, there's more! We've upgraded the weapons and the whole game animations are cooler.  

You'll feel every shot and swing like never before. & And guess what? New characters are joining the game. So, mark your calendars for Feb 25th from 6:00 PM to 9:00 PM (GMT+4) and get ready to experience StrayShot public beta! It's going to be epic!
